{"tid":1938910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"雙賊刀劫洪水橋油站　擸近2千元現金及手機","createTime":"2020-03-23T00:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T00:57:27.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05e783b1bed583b1b4ad2dbd7f0e3300bf484f01","tid":1938910,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T00:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsF1PtT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsF1PtT.jpg&h=fa6725b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過往曾有賊人行劫加德士油站。<br />\n<br />\n天水圍洪水橋石埗村加德士油站，今日(23日)凌晨3時許，2名男子闖進上址，各自亮出牛肉刀指嚇姓余(44歲)女職員表示打劫，搶去萁約1,700元現金及一部手機後逃去，職員報警。警員聞訊到場兜截惜無發現，正根據現場天眼片段及事主提供的資料追緝賊人。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查後將案件列行劫，交由元朗警區刑事調查隊接手調查，並追緝在逃賊人，2人年約20至30歲，身高約1.7米，中等身材，案發時戴帽及口罩。其中一人身穿黑色長袖上衣及藍色長褲，其同黨則身穿白色長袖上衣及藍色長褲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200323/mobile/bkn-20200323041644627-0323_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200323%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200323041644627-0323_00822_001.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=3124648d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200323/mobile/bkn-20200323041644627-0323_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ca04f3b254ed06384cc8add6c099a367095ecc8a","tid":1938910,"uid":216710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T00:19:09.000Z","msg":"流浮山刀手?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8b807d6e16d19a8a2f0f44b7d7ab208a8ad45c","tid":1938910,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05e783b1bed583b1b4ad2dbd7f0e3300bf484f01","tid":1938910,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T00:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsF1PtT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsF1PtT.jpg&h=fa6725b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過往曾有賊人行劫加德士油站。<br />\n<br />\n天水圍洪水橋石埗村加德士油站，今日(23日)凌晨3時許，2名男子闖進上址，各自亮